snippet.title: Horror Tales: The Beggar (PS5 Physical Edition)
snippet.description:
Horror Tales: The Beggar is the new horror game created by the solo developer Carlos Coronado.

Pre-Order now the PlayStation 5 Physical Edition created by Tesura Games:
https://store.tesuragames.com/producto/horror-tales-the-beggar-ps5/

Coming this year to all platforms. More info here:
https://www.jandusoft.com/thebeggar/
